  "<td valign=\"top\" width=\"25%\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\"><a href=\"/m13/en/124.html\">Chandra's Fury</a></span>\n        <p><img src=\"http://magiccards.info/images/en.gif\" alt=\"English\" width=\"16\" height=\"11\" class=\"flag2\"> Magic 2013, <i>Common</i></p>\n        \n          <p>Instant, \n            4R (5)</p>\n          <p class=\"ctext\"><b>Chandra's Fury deals 4 damage to target player and 1 damage to each creature that player controls.</b></p>\n        \n        <p><i>\"I asked if they wanted to do things the easy way. I meant easy for me.\"</i></p>\n        <p>Illus. Volkan Baga</p>\n    </td>",
